          <li><strong>PTE Core:</strong> $355 - $390 CAD</li>
          <li>
            <strong>TEF Canada (French):</strong> $390 - $450 CAD
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>TCF Canada (French):</strong> $350 - $400 CAD
